 First public release.

@ENDNODE
@NODE FUTURE "Future enhancements"
@{CODE}@{JCENTER}@{FG SHINE}W - o - r - d - M - a - n - i - a 

@{FG TEXT}Version : @{FG HIGHLIGHT}1.0
@{FG TEXT}Release Date : @{FG HIGHLIGHT}9 September 1996.@{FG TEXT}
@{JLEFT}
@{BG FILL}                                                                            @{BG BACK}

@{BODY}I'm  not  sure  whether I intend to develope WordMania much further, it does
pretty much everthing I wanted it to do.  However, if you want to see any of
the  following  features  added,  or  have  some  ideas  on improvements and
addtions to WordMania then please write and let me know.  I've never had any
comments  from users of previous programs that I've written, so I doubt that
this one will receive much mail, however I live in hope!


@{CODE}Possible Future Enchancements...

@{FG SHINE}@{U}Additions to the Criteria Window@{UU}

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  A list of letters that should NOT be in the result string.

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  Options to specify link letters. ie. First letter and fourth
    letter should be the same. etc.

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  Option to load and save the criteria.

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  Creating full length anagram strings. ie. converting someones name into
    a phrase.

@{FG SHINE}@{U}General Additions@{UU}

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  A Dictionaries Window with options for creating and maintaining
    dictionary files.

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  Amigaguide on-line help.

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  Inclusion of a special fast dictionary format, with compacted sections
    and offsets, etc. (This would help increase speed and reduce memory/disk
    space).

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  Font Sensitive GUI.

 @{FG FILL}o@{FG TEXT}  Cursor key control of the results list.

@ENDNODE
